    <section id="about" class="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Nadia Josephine Prescott is a young entrepreneur, author of the book <i>Hopeful Nets</i>, and a creative born on the Caribbean island of Saint Lucia and raised in New York. Her diverse background and multicultural lens can be seen throughout the perspectives of her work. She graduated from the University of Buckingham with a BA Honours in English Literature. An avid traveler, she's lived in many countries across the globe, and worked as an English teacher most recently in Hong Kong. She continues to share her passions for music, art, poetry, and literature, with every new experience and destination along life's journey.</p>
